China Halts Overseas Yuan Loans, CCTV Cites Caixin

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-08-01T05:15:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/china-halts-overseas-yuan-loans-cctv-cites-caixin-correct-.html
(Corrects source of news.)  China ’s central bank suspended
borrowing by domestic companies from overseas banks,  China
Central Television  reported today, citing a Caixin Weekly
magazine report, which cited a notice issued on July 18.  The People’s Bank of China also suspended borrowing by
foreign-invested companies in China to cover the difference
between their total investments and registered capitals,
according to the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
